high_descs: Turn around and then face the counter to the right of the sink where the coffee maker is.
Pick the mug up from under the coffee maker.
Turn around and cross the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the mug up again.
Go left and cross the room and turn to the right to face the small black table next to the counter.
Put the mug down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug down on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the coffee machine on the left.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn around, bring the mug to the microwave in the corner to the left.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Take the heated mug back across the room to the small black table in the right corner.
Put the heated mug on the small black table, left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the small black table, left of the tomato.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the coffee machine and look at it.
Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee machine.
Turn around and go to the table with the microwave in the corner of the room.
Microwave the cup and take it back out of the microwave.
Go to the black table on the opposite side of the room.
Place the cup to the left of the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved cup on a black table.
